Setup the virtualenv
# install virtualenvwrapper
mkvirtualenv perks
pip install -r requirements.txt


To setup the database

psql -d postgres
create user <your user> with password '<some passwors>';
create database perks;
grant all privileges on database perks to <your user>;
\q

workon perks
./db_tasks.py db upgrade head
./db_tasks.py create_admin <your_email_address>

Start the server
./run.py

Log in to the site as an admin

point browser to http://localhost:5000
log in with admin/password

import plans so employees may enroll
click on the admin tab
click on the import tab
browse to ./docs/data_import_example.xlsx
